column5: We will be there from 6/14 - 6/22; anyone else fish it? Our 7th time for great eyes.
Which white lake are you talking about. There are a few lakes in Ontario called white lake? Fisherman 1792
White Lake west of WAWA about 70 miles. Provincial park also there.
Fish it all the time. Love that lake! It does produce some great eyes. Wife said today that we can get a seasonal camp ground at the provincial park that is there. Fisherman 1792
We are from Marquette, MI; wish I was closer to rent a seasonal site. But I will settle for a week. We are camping pm site 129 from 6/14 - 6/21; stop by for a "libation"
Will do I'll be off work for a few days. Fisherman 1792
Did you take 2 MI guys out on your boat 2 years ago? We had engine problems and fished with he and his son. He worked with underground fresh air system.
